OL,3,CTrial of baby murder accused scheduled
OL,4,Cfor next year
OL,6,FA man accused of murdering his baby
OL,7,Fson six years ago has made his first
OL,8,Fcrown court appearance.
OL,10,FNiall Worsfold, 29, of Farrow Road,
OL,11,FLeeds, is charged with the murder of
OL,12,Fthe infant who was one month old at
OL,13,Fthe time.
OL,15,FWest Yorkshire Police said the baby,
OL,16,Fwhose name has not been released, died
OL,17,Fin hospital on 10 July 2020.
OL,19,FWorsfold has also been charged with
OL,20,Fone count of child cruelty.
