OL,3,CTrial of baby murder accused scheduled
OL,4,Cfor next year
OL,6,FA trial, which is expected to last up
OL,7,Fto four weeks, has been scheduled for
OL,8,F22 February next year.
OL,10,FWorsfold was remanded in custody until
OL,11,Fhis plea and trial preparation hearing
OL,12,Fat the same court on 7 September.
OL,14,FJudge Howard Crowson said: "I think
OL,15,Fyou already know what's alleged
OL,16,Fagainst you in pretty clear terms."
OL,18,FA 25-year-old woman, who was arrested
OL,19,Fas part of the investigation, has been
OL,20,Freleased with no further action.
